{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"0b8828fc-96a5-495b-affd-19e082841e7f","content":"I can help guide you through analyzing your .NET crash dump. Here's how to approach it:\n\n**Tools for analysis** (depending on your environment):\n\n| Tool | Platform | Install |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| `dotnet-dump analyze` | Cross-platform | `dotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump` |\n| WinDbg + SOS | Windows | Part of Windows SDK |\n| `lldb` + SOS | Linux/macOS | `dotnet-sos install` after installing SOS |\n\n**Key commands once loaded** (using `dotnet-dump analyze <file.dmp>`):\n\n```\nclrstack          # managed call stack of crashing thread\npe                # print last exception\ndumpheap -stat    # heap overview\nthreads           # list all managed threads\nsetthread <id>    # switch threads, then clrstack again\nclrstack -all     # all managed thread stacks\n```\n\n**Typical workflow:**\n1. Open the dump with `dotnet-dump analyze your.dmp`\n2. Run `pe` to check for an unhandled exception\n3. Run `threads` → inspect each thread's `clrstack`\n4. Look for `StackOverflowException`, `OutOfMemoryException`, `AccessViolationException`, or your app's code in the stack\n\n---\n\nWould you like me to:\n- **Analyze the dump directly** — upload or provide the path to your `.dmp` file and I'll run the commands here\n- **Walk you through it step-by-step** on your own machine\n\nWhich do you prefer?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"99ce0341-8695-44f7-b665-de17432a6eb6","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a .dmp crash dump file from a .NET application and wants to analyze it to find the root cause of a crash. Let me help them with this.\n\nLooking at the available skills, I don't see a specific skill for analyzing .dmp files. The \"dump-collect\" skill is specifically for *collecting* dumps, not analyzing them. Let me help the user directly with guidance on analyzing their dump file.\n\nLet me check what tools are available in the environment first.","outputTokens":488,"requestId":"980C:18FEB2:597D83A:620B432:69F40800"},"id":"6ecfaaa0-fb3e-459c-b3e1-3d22c1a8bca4","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:55:24.416Z","parentId":"b6e799db-7f03-4f26-bf40-fa19acee0f6f"}
